title: Ancient Herbalist
summary: Ancient Herbalist Manhua I Qin Feng, God of Alchemy knows as Pill Emperor died fighting demons invading Divine Continent but when I opened my eyes, I was reborn 100,000 years in the past. In my previous Life I couldn’t practice Martial Arts but in this life, I shall achieve the Pinnacle of both Martial Arts and Pill Refining, revive my family and protect the Human Race from the Demons at all cost. ”A journey to change the Past and make a Better Future, to protect the humanity” Ancient Herbalist, Rebirth of the Peerless Alchemist, 绝世丹神, Jue Shi Dan Shen, Peerless Dan God, Peerless Pill God, The Ultimate God of Alchemy
